The last time [Dm]I held her hand
[G7]Her touch was autumn spring and summer and [C]winter too
The last time [Dm]I let go of her
[G7]She walked away into the night I [F]lost her in the [G7]misty streets
[F]A thousand months a [G7]thousand years when [F]other lips will [G7]kiss her eyes
